    "pill": "Our story",
    "title1": "We believe padel deserves",
    "titleHighlight": "professional tools",
    "intro": "We are players and technology professionals passionate about padel. We built WhinPadel after seeing clubs needing a modern platform to organize tournaments without the usual headaches.",
